docs.text:
Parameter Type Required Description <code>q</code> string Yes City name (e.g., Paris) <code>appid</code> string Yes Your API key <p>Example Request:</p> <p>https://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/forecast?q=Paris&amp;appid={YOUR_API_KEY}</p> <p>Response Example:</p> <pre><code>{
  "city": {
    "name": "Paris",
    "country": "FR"
  },
  "list": [
    {
      "dt_txt": "2025-10-05 12:00:00",
      "main": {
        "temp": 289.92,
        "humidity": 82
      },
      "weather": [
        {
          "description": "light rain",
          "icon": "10d"
        }
      ],
      "wind": {
        "speed": 4.1
      }
    }
    // ...more 3-hour intervals
  ]
}
</code></pre>
